{
  "text": "The symmetry of the backreaction problem tells us that the components of the one form field strength along the flat directions vanish: \u2202 \u00b5 \u03c7 = 0. The remaining modes \u2202 \u03b8\u00b1\u03c1 \u03c7 are constructed [CITATION_1] from the spin fields such that there is zero spin in the flat four directions and the U (1) R charge of the N = 2 algebra on the cigar is Q = ",
